nodes.text: Ash-rabbits were a species of rabbit found throughout the galaxy. One type of ash-rabbit was the Sullustan ash-rabbit, which was native to Sullust. They were small and herbivorous, eating food such as marsh-fruit. While on an uncharted swampworld, Milo Graf attempted to capture an ash-rabbit, although he feared that his sister Lina's happabore-like blundering would scare it away.
